OL,3,CDepartment of Health defends #188,000
OL,4,Csalary of new boss
OL,6,FA member of Stormont's Health
OL,7,FCommittee described the salary as "eye-
OL,8,Fwatering", especially at a time of
OL,9,Fimmense budget pressures.
OL,11,FSDLP MLA Colin McGrath said he
OL,12,Fbelieves that the state of Northern
OL,13,FIreland's health service has become
OL,14,F"so bad", that the Department of
OL,15,FHealth is having to "pay way over the
OL,16,Fodds for someone to fix our problems".
