OL,4,Csalary of new boss
OL,6,FHe added: "If we are going to pay top
OL,7,Fdollar for somebody, we want to ensure
OL,8,Fthere are results quick because
OL,9,Fpatients are the most important people
OL,10,Fin this whole process."
OL,12,FDUP Health Committee member Diane
OL,13,FDodds has said that Mr Farrar will
OL,14,Fhave to prove that he is worth the
OL,15,Fsalary.
OL,17,F"It's a huge amount of money and we
OL,18,Fwill only see in time whether that
OL,19,Fwill be justified," Mrs Dodds said.
