OL,9,Fto drive reform, give us better
OL,10,Foutcomes, then that is very important."
OL,12,FThe Department of Health defended the
OL,13,Fsalary, saying "Mike Farrar has a long
OL,14,Fand impressive track record of health
OL,15,Fservice leadership in the United
OL,16,FKingdom and brings considerable
OL,17,Fexperience of healthcare systems in
OL,18,Fthis country and overseas.
